asset.hookText: http://www.skis.com/Rossignol-Krypto-MagTek-Snowboard-2013/280922P,default,pd.html  The Rossignol Krypto MagTek won the award for Outsider Gear of the Year for 2012 with the title of Quiver of One. The Krypto MagTek is an effortless ride that allows people to truly enjoy the all-mountain experience. With a super directional flex it allows the snowboard to have a more mellower flex then its bring brother the Experience MagTek. With Magnetraction 7M the Krypto has contact points on each side of the board, resulting in amazing control regardless of snow conditions. The Krypto MagTek is the perfect board for any rider looking to explore the mountain but when style comes into play be able to thrown down in the park with anyone.
